dimensions: Warp x Weft: 31.8 x 61.6 cm (12 1/2 x 24 1/4 in.)
title: Rayamex Stripe
description: Plain weave with vertical stripes of black, white, tan, blue and violet. Groups of thin stripes in black and tan and black and white alternate with wider stripes of white and violet and blue and black. White weft threads intersect with warp threads of black, violet, tan and blue to give a variegated appearance to the surface. Number 1251.
